    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [300ml]<strong> </span>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>sultanas </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>sultana stock</strong></p>",
