    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the <strong>vegetable parcel[s]</strong> in the oven for 12-15 min or until tender – this is your <strong>buttery veg</strong></p><p>Once the chicken has browned all over, reduce the heat to medium-high and add your <strong>curry powder</strong> with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min or until fragrant, then add the <strong>sultana stock</strong> and mix it all together</p><p>Cook for 5-6 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
