        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>When the pastry is nearly ready, add your <strong>mango chutney </strong>to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, give everything a good mix up and cook for 1-2 min over a medium heat</p><p>Reduce the heat to very low and add your <strong>soured cream</strong></p><p>Mix it all together and cook for 1-2 min or until warmed through (don't let it boil!) – this is your <strong>coronation chicken pie mix</strong></p>",
